    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300077173_16_13370-13436",
      "chapterUid": 16,
      "range": "13370-13436",
      "markText": "就到这里吧，因为分别的时候到啦，虽然我就要赴死，你们还会继续活，但我们双方究竟哪个命数更好，谁又能知道？——呜呼，厥知惟[a5]神！",
      "totalCount": 1120,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300077173&chapterUid=16&rangeStart=13370&rangeEnd=13436",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b4a322d0813ab84a5g013c2d?chapterUid=16&rangeStart=13370&rangeEnd=13436"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300077173_11_7983-8055",
      "chapterUid": 11,
      "range": "7983-8055",
      "markText": "居然只去关心如何才能赚取尽可能多的钱财、[29e]名望和荣誉，却既不关心也不思考明智、真理以及如何让灵魂尽可能变得最好，难道你们就不感到羞愧吗？",
      "totalCount": 1110,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300077173&chapterUid=11&rangeStart=7983&rangeEnd=8055",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b4a322d0813ab84a5g013c2d?chapterUid=11&rangeStart=7983&rangeEnd=8055"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300077173_8_12307-12364",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "12307-12364",
      "markText": "凡夫俗子们，你们中随便什么人，只要能像苏格拉底那样认识到，自己在智慧方面真正说来毫无价值，那么，他就是最智慧的人”",
      "totalCount": 954,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300077173&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=12307&rangeEnd=12364",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b4a322d0813ab84a5g013c2d?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=12307&rangeEnd=12364"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300077173_8_10839-10905",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "10839-10905",
      "markText": "由于能出色地完成本行的手艺活，每个人就号称自己在别的最重大的事情上也都最智慧。他们这种离谱的大错反而[22e]遮蔽了自己的那种巧智。",
      "totalCount": 800,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300077173&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=10839&rangeEnd=10905",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b4a322d0813ab84a5g013c2d?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=10839&rangeEnd=10905"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300077173_15_8259-8277",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "8259-8277",
      "markText": "对人而言，缺乏省察的生活根本不值得过",
      "totalCount": 736,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300077173&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=8259&rangeEnd=8277",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b4a322d0813ab84a5g013c2d?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=8259&rangeEnd=8277"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300077173_8_10002-10030",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "10002-10030",
      "markText": "因为他们虽说了很多美妙的话，其实并不理解自己所说的东西。",
      "totalCount": 684,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300077173&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=10002&rangeEnd=10030",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b4a322d0813ab84a5g013c2d?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=10002&rangeEnd=10030"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300077173_15_627-711",
      "chapterUid": 15,
      "range": "627-711",
      "markText": "但他为什么要故意激怒陪审团，处处跟同胞们作对，主动“找死”，或许反对他和支持他的人都不理解。的确，这不是一次成功的“申辩”，却无疑是西方思想史上最成功最生动的“教谕”。",
      "totalCount": 663,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300077173&chapterUid=15&rangeStart=627&rangeEnd=711",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b4a322d0813ab84a5g013c2d?chapterUid=15&rangeStart=627&rangeEnd=711"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300077173_6_3759-3837",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "3759-3837",
      "markText": "无论我的说话方式好也罢、歹也罢，都请只考虑这样一点，并把心思转到这一点上，即看[a5]我说的究竟正当与否——因为这才是法官的职责，而演说者之德则在于讲真话。",
      "totalCount": 615,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300077173&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3759&rangeEnd=3837",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b4a322d0813ab84a5g013c2d?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=3759&rangeEnd=3837"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300077173_8_8083-8151",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "8083-8151",
      "markText": "遵从那位神明做了一番探究之后，我发现那些名气最大的人，几乎都最差劲，[a5]而另外那些看上去更低贱的人，却因为明智，反倒更平和持中一些。",
      "totalCount": 612,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300077173&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=8083&rangeEnd=8151",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b4a322d0813ab84a5g013c2d?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=8083&rangeEnd=8151"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300077173_12_1602-1648",
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "range": "1602-1648",
      "markText": "美德不来自钱财，相反，钱财以及世人其他所有好东西，无论私人生活还是公共生活中的，都来自美德。",
      "totalCount": 570,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300077173&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=1602&rangeEnd=1648",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b4a322d0813ab84a5g013c2d?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=1602&rangeEnd=1648"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300077173_8_14788-14803",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "14788-14803",
      "markText": "他们虽假装知道，其实一无所知。",
      "totalCount": 540,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300077173&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=14788&rangeEnd=14803",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b4a322d0813ab84a5g013c2d?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=14788&rangeEnd=14803"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300077173_5_948-1031",
      "chapterUid": 5,
      "range": "948-1031",
      "markText": "最终，苏格拉底不愿意通过苦苦哀求和装可怜等方式博取陪审团的同情而获释，因为这与他的人生信条不合。当然，这也是为了不给陪审团添麻烦，免得他们违背司法誓言而做出不义之举。",
      "totalCount": 490,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300077173&chapterUid=5&rangeStart=948&rangeEnd=1031",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b4a322d0813ab84a5g013c2d?chapterUid=5&rangeStart=948&rangeEnd=1031"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300077173_6_6038-6086",
      "chapterUid": 6,
      "range": "6038-6086",
      "markText": "他们在你们最容易轻信的年龄就对你们说那些话，因为你们中的一些人当时还是小孩子，有些人也只是小伙子",
      "totalCount": 468,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300077173&chapterUid=6&rangeStart=6038&rangeEnd=6086",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b4a322d0813ab84a5g013c2d?chapterUid=6&rangeStart=6038&rangeEnd=6086"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300077173_8_15844-15880",
      "chapterUid": 8,
      "range": "15844-15880",
      "markText": "总而言之，对于最先控告我的人所控告的罪名，这就是在你们面前的充分辩护了。",
      "totalCount": 459,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300077173&chapterUid=8&rangeStart=15844&rangeEnd=15880",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b4a322d0813ab84a5g013c2d?chapterUid=8&rangeStart=15844&rangeEnd=15880"
    },
    {
