      "chapterUid": 3,
      "range": "857-913",
      "markText": "自有柏拉图书，借用我国古人的说法，可谓“天地已洩其秘，而浑穆醇庞之气，人日由其中而不知是道寄于人，而学寄于天”。",
      "totalCount": 450,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300077173&chapterUid=3&rangeStart=857&rangeEnd=913",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b4a322d0813ab84a5g013c2d?chapterUid=3&rangeStart=857&rangeEnd=913"
    },
    {
